{"tid":2105713,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母，700 又派股份俾 IT 狗，喺廢港做 IT 狗乜柒都冇","createTime":"2020-07-12T23:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T16:35:08.000Z","uid":125976,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c6dfacdf531f84f050872c2210080a10d56ed3","tid":2105713,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T23:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7月10日，騰訊在港交所公告了最新的股權激勵計劃，擬授予不少於2.97萬人2664萬的股份。<br />\n這意味着人均可獲得897股騰訊股票，以騰訊最新收盤價546.5港元計算，人均獲獎勵股份市值約49.02萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n面向員工的股權激勵有「金手銬」一説。作為科技公司重要的資源，核心人才的股權激勵在科技公司中並不少見，在A股尤其是科創板公司中，近來均有推出鉅額股權激勵計劃；與之相應，面向骨幹人才推出令人豔羨的股權激勵的同時，也推出了多樣化的嚴厲考核。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc3654668538d13fa10b1cb74ad7090d50654af","tid":2105713,"uid":159435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T23:33:38.000Z","msg":"你靠買700都執咗唔少啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64dc6661594f9f53ec24ee10e5c2c709ef7323b","tid":2105713,"uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T23:36:13.000Z","msg":"唔止700<br />\n成日聽支那公司派錢派車仲派樓<br />\n香港得個double pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c40c511f210c7d4256183305092d537b15fb14","tid":2105713,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T23:38:29.000Z","msg":"700搞咁耐先升得100點左右 是但一隻美股波動%都勁過佢"},{"pid":"a9e77a7141b6be42003e7e97fd3fb277b5ab778b","tid":2105713,"uid":125976,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e64dc66